<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WMS 智慧倉儲管理系統｜流通科技專題</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
  <script id="MathJax-script" async src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-chtml.js"></script>
  <style>
    :root { 
      --bg: #fffaf4; --ink: #3d332d; --peach: #ff9f7d; --sakura: #ffb7cf; --caramel: #d7ad79;
    }
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; }
    
    .btn-action { padding: 12px 24px; background: var(--peach); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
    .btn-action:hover { background: var(--caramel); }
    
    .input-group { margin: 20px 0; display: flex; gap: 10px; }
    .input-field { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; flex: 1; }

    @media print { .no-print { display: none; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <header style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;" class="no-print">
      <h1>iWMS 智慧倉儲系統專題</h1>
      <button class="btn-action" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ 列印報告</button>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="content">
        <h2>庫存最佳化核心模型</h2>
        <p>透過數據驅動的決策模型，優化訂購與庫存持有成本。</p>
        
        <div id="eoq-math">$$EOQ = \sqrt{\frac{2DS}{H}}$$</div>
        
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="number" id="D" class="input-field" placeholder="年度需求量 D">
          <input type="number" id="S" class="input-field" placeholder="訂購成本 S">
          <input type="number" id="H" class="input-field" placeholder="持有成本 H">
          <button class="btn-action" onclick="calc()">計算最適量</button>
        </div>
        <div id="result" style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;"></div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <h2>技術趨勢影片</h2>
        <div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
          <iframe style="position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GI5jxp4rtEs" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script>
    function calc() {
      const D = document.getElementById('D').value;
      const S = document.getElementById('S').value;
      const H = document.getElementById('H').value;
      if (D && S && H) {
        const eoq = Math.sqrt((2 * D * S) / H);
        document.getElementById('result').innerHTML = `計算結果：最適訂購批量 (EOQ) 為 ${eoq.toFixed(2)} 件`;
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
